(658, 'Red object detection - (MATLAB)', 'Tania Kapoor', '<p style="text-align: justify;">The Red object detection system is designed using the image processing toolbox in MATLAB. It can detect red color objects . The thing which is distinctive about this system is that it is quite easily assessible system &nbsp;and can be implemented anywhere just with a laptop having a inbuilt camera. In the recent times, the use of image processing has grown exponentially and that escalates even more the demand of such a system.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;This project is designed using the webcam of the laptop and gives the desired output accordingly after all the processing. At the same time, its capability can be increased to a level at which it can detect &nbsp;different &nbsp;coloured objects and process applications accordingly. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The project works as follows:- the red objects are extracted from the RGB image and then the centroid of the objects is found . This project is limited to only 2 objects but can be extended to any number . The centroid is used to draw a rectangular frame which is cropped and previewed in the same window. Only the effective area bounded by red objects is cropped. Such an application can be used for surveillance and other security purposes.</p>', '<div style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The room in which project is run should have a good light source.</li>\r\n<li>A proper good red colored bands should be used.</li>\r\n<li>The distance between the web cam and your hands should not be more than 40-50 cms.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/tania-kapoor-19735a105', 'Elecbits_software_red.jpg', 'https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B9kR8Q3EsyKVSkZicExMV0pXN0U', 'https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B9kR8Q3EsyKVSkZicExMV0pXN0U', 'softwaretest.png'),
(2, 'GUI Calculator -[MATLAB]', 'Tania Kapoor', '<p style="text-align: justify;">It is a simple GUI calculator designed using image processing toolbox in MATLAB. It can perform simple arithmetic operation like addition, multiplication, subtraction and division. The interface is quite user Friendly and it is very easy to operate. You can make your own calculator sitting at home by just having a laptop and a MATLAB software.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>', '<p style="text-align: justify;">In this project the user has to choose two values for the operation and then has to select the arithmetic operation that he wants to perform, after that he needs to click on &lsquo;=&rsquo; and hence the answer will be shown. User can also perform other mathematic operation like logarithmic, exponential, trigonometric ratio, percentage etc.</p>', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/tania-kapoor-19735a105', 'Elecbits_Matlab_calculator.jpg', 'https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B9kR8Q3EsyKVdjl3N2V6YlkxQW8', NULL, NULL),
(3, 'FACE DETECTION - [MATLAB]', 'Tania Kapoor', '<p style="text-align: justify;">Skin regions are extracted using a set of bounding rules based on the skin colour. Distribution obtained from a training set. The segment face regions are further classified using a parallel combination of simple morphological operations. Experimental result on a larger data set have demonstrated that the proposed RGB model is able to achieve good detection success rates for near frontal faces of varying orientation, skin colour and background environment.&nbsp;</p>', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;">To run this program a webcam inbuilt laptop or a pc with external webcam attached is required. It is a MATLAB project for face detection using RGB skin colour model. This model will enable to detect the face of user who will be running this MATLAB program at that point of time.</p>', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/tania-kapoor-19735a105', 'Elecbits_face_detection.jpg', 'https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B9kR8Q3EsyKVaU9VNEJNTHVGZlE', NULL, NULL);
